	    <h1>{code} ↦ CodeRippa ↦ {PDF}</h1>
	    <p class="pitch">
				<%= image_tag "ripit.png" %><br/>
				Convert <em>any</em> source code into a <em>beautiful</em> PDF. Works on almost <em>150+</em> languages, with customizable <em>30+</em> themes!</p>
			<div>
			</div>
	    <p class="github-info">
	      <a href="https://github.com/benjamintanweihao/CodeRippa" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">View project on GitHub</a>
	      <a class="btn btn-large btn-warning">Download a sample</a>
	      <a class="btn btn-large btn-danger">Learn more</a>

	    </p>
	  </div>
