	<div class="promo">
		<h1 class="promo">Be a better programmer.</h1>
		<p class="marketing-byline">(Or why CodeRippa exists.)</p>
		<p class="gospel">
			We don't take the time to study the code written by the <em>masters</em>. I have absolutely no idea how <em>vim</em> works, neither do I know all the magic that goes behind <em>Rails</em>, or how <em>Coffee-script</em> is written in <em>Coffee-script</em> and <em>Rubinus</em> is written in <em>Ruby</em> ... You get the idea.<br/><br/> <strong>CodeRippa</strong> is my attempt to make source code reading a more pleasurable experience, and help programmers get better at their craft.
		</p>
