				</p>
	    </div>
			<div class="span4">
				<h2>Eye-Candy</h2>
 				<p class="promo-desc">
					Choose from over 30+ TextMate themes: Cobalt, Mac Classic, Sunburst, Twilight, VibrantInk ...
				</p>
	    </div>
	    <div class="span4">
				<h2>Language Support</h2>
 				<p class="promo-desc">
					Actionscript, C, Erlang, Haskell, Ruby, Python, Prolog ... CodeRippa can handle it all.
				</p>
	    </div>
			<hr class="soften">
  	</div><!--/row-->
	</div><!--/promo>->
